                                            <a href="//bbs.rong360.com/thread-211159-1.html" ra-click="apply" data-pagename="credit_pc_cardDetail_forum" target="_blank">秒批！异地APP申卡， ...</a>
                                                                                        <img src="/static/img/credit/img_forum.png" width="14" height="14" alt="图">
